query_text: What is stock turnover ratio?
agent_generated_sql:
SELECT p.sku, p.product_type, SUM(s.products_sold) / NULLIF(AVG(p.stock_levels), 0) AS stock_turnover_ratio

GROUP BY p.sku, p.product_type
ORDER BY stock_turnover_ratio DESC
LIMIT 100

query_text: Show me year-over-year sales growth by category
agent_generated_sql:
SELECT p.category, o.year, SUM(o.sales) as total_sales, 
             (SUM(o.sales) - LAG(SUM(o.sales)) OVER (PARTITION BY p.category ORDER BY o.year)) / NULLIF(LAG(SUM(o.sales)) OVER (PARTITION BY p.category ORDER BY o.year), 0) * 100 as yoy_growth
     FROM spend_data.orders o
     JOIN spend_data.products p ON o.product_id = p.product_id
     GROUP BY p.category, o.year
     ORDER BY p.category, o.year

query_text: Which products have high demand but low stock from Supplier 2?
agent_generated_sql:
SELECT p.sku, p.product_type, p.stock_levels, s.products_sold, sc.supplier_id 
FROM demand_data.products p 
JOIN demand_data.sales s ON p.sku = s.sku 
JOIN demand_data.supply_chain sc ON p.sku = sc.sku 
WHERE sc.supplier_id = 2 AND p.stock_levels < 20 AND s.products_sold > 100 
ORDER BY s.products_sold DESC, p.stock_levels ASC 
LIMIT 100
